{"title":"Readers’ Rides: Christopher’s Salsa Fargo Prepped for the North Central Washington 250","link":"https://theradavist.com/2021/07/readers-rides-christophers-salsa-fargo-prepped-for-the-north-central-washington-250/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=readers-rides-christophers-salsa-fargo-prepped-for-the-north-central-washington-250","date":1625835629000,"content":"<p>This week’s Readers’ Rides is <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/pedal_pedal_pedal_/\" target=\"_blank\">Christopher</a>‘s Salsa Fargo all loaded down for the North Central Washington 250. Check out all the frame specs and some of Christopher’s photos below!<span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/07/DSC_6418.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/07/DSC_6423.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Here is my 2010 Salsa Fargo 1. It has morphed several times over the past 5 years. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/07/DSC_6427.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/07/DSC_6428.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/07/DSC_6429.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>I converted to singlespeed about a year ago with my First Components eccentric BB. I have it in racing mode and prepped for the North Central Washington 250.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/07/DSC_6414.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/07/DSC_6417.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/07/DSC_6425.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Revelate bags<br />\nProfile airstryke aero bars<br />\nGarmin etrex 30x<br />\nSelle SMP saddle<br />\nForager cycle cable cherries in green<br />\nSpot gen3<br />\nKenda 29 x 2” (tubes)<br />\nOne Up 36t chainring<br />\nSurly 21t cog<br />\nSP dynamo hub<br />\nSinewave Beacon front light</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/07/DSC_6436.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/07/DSC_6437.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/07/DSC_6442.jpeg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" /></p>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"77413e9143eb0b8ac0ac943533a364692d869d8629ae61e6f8eff53fbcf666b2","category":"Cycling"}